name: South_Shore_Axess_5-Shelf_Narrow_Bookcase
reviews: great shelf for a narrow space. Good, solid construction and attractive finish.

I ordered this one along with the wider one, unfortunately this one had a broken side wall. I have since returned the item and received a full refund. Easy return process. These are nice bookcases and as it turned out I could fit another wide one so I ordered another one.
This is a good size for a narrow bookshelf, but the finishing caps for the screws break very easily and look cheap and there was a scratch on the finish that I didn't see until I put it together.
